dcterms:creator: Catherine Byers
dcterms:description: A single speaker high-quality English dataset of audiobook recordings by Catherine Byers (the speaker from the 2013 Blizzard Challenge). This dataset consists of 147 hours of recordings of 49 books, read in an animated and emotive storytelling style.
dcterms:title: Single-speaker dataset

dcterms:description: A proprietary high-quality English speech dataset consisting of 296 hours across 44 speakers (5 with Australian accents, 6 with British accents, 1 with an Indian accent, 2 with Singaporean accents, and 30 with United States accents).
dcterms:title: Multi-speaker dataset
